com.yantra.interop.client

Interface ClientVersionSupport


  • public interface ClientVersionSupport
    To support Client version, any class implementing "YFSEnvironment", should also implement this interface. All the `Request headers` are set as a HashMap

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      java.util.HashMap getClientProperties()
      Returns all the properties set at request Headers.
      void setClientProperties(java.util.HashMap properties)
      Sets all the properties set at request Headers as a HashMap.

    • Method Detail

      • getClientProperties

        java.util.HashMap getClientProperties()
        Returns all the properties set at request Headers. Any properties set by Client using RCP PCAs can be recovered from this method. Should be used by API/Service if their logic varied from one client version to other.

      • setClientProperties

        void setClientProperties(java.util.HashMap properties)
        Sets all the properties set at request Headers as a HashMap. Any properties set by Client using RCP PCAs are set also set here.
        properties - client properties can be passed here.
